improved_metadata.title: Barbershop Mayhem: The Reverse Mohawk Saga
improved_metadata.description: This track paints a chaotic scene inside a barbershop, highlighting a disastrous haircut experience and the ensuing social media frenzy. It's a frenetic narrative driven by sharp imagery and dark humor.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Trust me, bro, the biggest lie of the year, like the reverse mohawk, man, his future unclear
